        <h2>Children's Privacy / 儿童隐私</h2>
        <p>
            We comply with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act. We do not knowingly collect personal information on children under the age of 13.
            <span class="lang-zh">我们遵守《儿童在线隐私保护法》。我们不会故意收集 13 岁以下儿童的个人信息。</span>
